menu "Board driver options"

config APP_MQTT_ENABLE
    bool "Enable MQTT integration in board drivers"
    default y
    help
        When enabled, DI/DO/LED/buzzer drivers publish and subscribe over MQTT.
        Disable for firmwares without an MQTT broker (e.g. Matter-only builds).

config APP_SNTP_ENABLE
    bool "Enable SNTP time synchronisation"
    default y
    help
        Periodically sync the system clock from an NTP server and mirror each
        sync to the battery-backed RTC.  Disable for firmwares that do not need
        accurate local time (e.g. Matter-only builds).

config APP_SCRIPTING_ENABLE
    bool "Enable scripting engine callbacks"
    default n
    help
        Internal: set by the full firmware when the rule engine is present.
        Enables scripting_on_time_sync() call in sntp_sync.c.

endmenu
